<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="14Jun1938"><font color="red">14 June 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Richard de la Mere to Paul L&eacute;on): I have now had the new drawing made of the short passage of music for WORK IN PROGRESS and I am sending it on to you, before getting the block made, just in order to make quite sure that no errors have crept in &hellip; show it to Mr Joyce. </div>
